OL,3,CWelsh Government-owned Powys farm now
OL,4,Cworth half a million pounds less
OL,6,FThe Welsh Government made "avoidable
OL,7,Fmistakes" during the "rushed" purchase
OL,8,Fof a Powys farm that is now worth half
OL,9,Fa million pounds less than it cost,
OL,10,Faccording to a report by the Senedd's
OL,11,Fwatchdog committee.
OL,13,FGilestone Farm, near Talybont-on-Usk,
OL,14,Fwas bought in 2022 for #4.25m, as part
OL,15,Fof a plan to secure the future of the
OL,16,FGreen Man Festival, a plan that was
OL,17,Ffinally scuppered when nesting ospreys
OL,18,Fwere discovered on the site.
