OL,3,CWelsh Government-owned Powys farm now
OL,4,Cworth half a million pounds less
OL,6,FThe Welsh Government insists that it
OL,7,Ffollowed "proper processes" in buying
OL,8,Fthe farm and that it continues to
OL,9,Fexplore "potential opportunities for
OL,10,Fits future use".
OL,12,FMark Isherwood, who chairs the Public
OL,13,FAccounts and Public Administration
OL,14,Fcommittee, said: "The Committee is
OL,15,Fdeeply concerned by the Welsh
OL,16,FGovernment's handling of the purchase
OL,17,Fof Gilestone Farm.
