OL,3,CWelsh Government-owned Powys farm now
OL,4,Cworth half a million pounds less
OL,6,F"While we recognise the importance of
OL,7,Facting swiftly to support the creative
OL,8,Fsector, this decision was taken with
OL,9,Favoidable haste and without the
OL,10,Fthorough due diligence that the public
OL,11,Frightly expects. It raises serious
OL,12,Fquestions about internal processes and
OL,13,Fthe robustness of governance
OL,14,Fstructures.
OL,16,F"Furthermore, the Welsh Government
OL,17,Fmust do more to ensure that
OL,18,Fcommunities are not only consulted but
OL,19,Fgenuinely listened to. Engagement must
OL,20,Fbe meaningful, inclusive, and
OL,21,Fconsistent.
OL,26,@xD@AOU
