OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F468A1753799017
OL,3,CWelsh Government-owned Powys farm now
OL,4,Cworth half a million pounds less
OL,6,F"The significant loss in the value of
OL,7,Fthe property is particularly notable
OL,8,Fin the current financial climate, and
OL,9,Fwe expect the Welsh Government to
OL,10,Fclarify its future intentions for the
OL,11,Fsite and to set out how it will
OL,12,Fmitigate the financial loss to the
OL,13,Fpublic purse.
OL,15,F"To ensure lessons are learned, the
OL,16,FCommittee will want to carry out
OL,17,Ffurther work looking at the Welsh
OL,18,FGovernment's approach to property
OL,19,Finvestments, to assess whether current
OL,20,Fprocesses are sufficiently rigorous
OL,21,Fand fit for purpose."
