OL,4,Cworth half a million pounds less
OL,6,FThe Welsh Government will now consider
OL,7,Fthe report and issue its response. A
OL,8,Fspokesperson said: "Gilestone Farm was
OL,9,Facquired in 2022, following proper
OL,10,Fprocesses and in keeping with market
OL,11,Fvalues at the time, in order to
OL,12,Fsupport the growth of the Creative
OL,13,FSector in Wales and a stronger Mid-
OL,14,FWales economy.
