OL,3,CWelsh Government-owned Powys farm now
OL,4,Cworth half a million pounds less
OL,6,F"We were delighted to learn in August
OL,7,F2023 of the arrival of the pair of
OL,8,Fmating ospreys, which returned in
OL,9,F2024, and again this year. Their first
OL,10,Fegg hatched in early June 2025. This
OL,11,Fis believed to be a first for the Usk
OL,12,FValley in at least 250 years and marks
OL,13,Fan important milestone in the
OL,14,Fprotection of this important species.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
