OL,4,Cworth half a million pounds less
OL,6,FThe Welsh Conservatives have renewed
OL,7,Ftheir criticism in the wake of today's
OL,8,Freport. Brecon and Radnorshire MS,
OL,9,FJames Evans, said: "The purchase of
OL,10,FGilestone Farm should never have
OL,11,Fhappened in the first place and the
OL,12,Fprocess around its purchase raises
OL,13,Fserious questions about Welsh
OL,14,FGovernment internal procedures.
OL,16,F"The Labour Government has spent
OL,17,Fmillions without a full, open
OL,18,Ftendering process or meaningful
OL,19,Fengagement with the community. Public
OL,20,Ffunds must be spent with care and due
OL,21,Fdiligence.
OL,26,@xD@AOU
