OL,6,F"The next time the Labour Government
OL,7,Freaches for the cheque book, they
OL,8,Fshould listen to local concerns and
OL,9,Fact with far greater transparency. In
OL,10,Fthe meantime, Gilestone Farm remains
OL,11,Fthe most expensive publicly owned
OL,12,F'bird nest' in history."
